This is a sample landing page

This hero section have been built using the integrated block editor.
Each section of this page can be edited and customized with ease using the integrated style editor or also using TailwindCSS as it has been integrated natively into the block editor.

The block editor has also been enabled with autosave (every 5 seconds)!
No need to remember to click the save button!

All forms and other elements are supported too.
With the power of JS you can also freely customize them to fit your needs, load custom pages, interact with API and more!
